The following file contains all of the necessary components to build a 7 inch touch screen display for the V-Core 3. 

BOM

1- Sunflounder 7" Touch Screen Display - https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07Y889J3X?psc=1&ref=ppx_yo2_dt_b_product_details
1- 45 Degree HDMI Adapter - https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00Y7UT6EK/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_title_o00_s00?ie=UTF8&psc=1
1- 45 Degree HDMI Cable (Down Angle) - https://www.amazon.com/gp/product/B00Y7UT6EK/ref=ppx_yo_dt_b_asin_title_o00_s00?ie=UTF8&psc=1
6- 3x4.6x5.7mm Heat Sets - https://www.amazon.com/dp/B087NBYF65?psc=1&ref=ppx_yo2_dt_b_product_details
1- Touch Screen Back Plate
1- Touch Screen Front Plate
4- M3x0.5x14 Socket Head Allen Screws
